			I agree, I recently found a short sword on a dead guard in freeport (the equivelent of finding a wallet!) and had been using a tarnished Bastard sword.  Being the Paladin I am, I really would prefer a long sword, so will use the short sword until a save up a few more plat to afford one, and trade it in.  Also, the short sword gets an average of 8 points of damage in a wack, vs my Bas sword that got in 12 or so, BUT the delay for the short sword is almost half of the Tarn Bas sword, so in reality, I'm getting in about 16 points of damage in to the 12 I got with the Tarn bas.  I do plan on upgrading soon though, still a decent interim weapon.
